settings.description:
Caves... filled with bats and moles! don't forget the iconic buzzy beetles as well!

shame there's no cave ceiling tiles though.
Chargin' Chucks lead their fellow Bob-ombs into this tight, grassy water filled course.
I didn't actually create this level, a relative did.
Venture through a switch-and-money-filled world of speedrunning, careful timing, precise jumps, and more! There's also an E-Coin up high in space, waiting to be found!
When were there so many pipes in the sky? Who knows, but for whatever reason Mario needs to get through all the piranhas and koopas.

This level has a secret exit.
Climb down a mountain while starting on the right part of the level
My First Level! So This is a fun level to play. There's also a secret ending by going to the chest. To do this, you have to step on the note blocks, Step on P-switch, and run to the chest.

A flood has happened in Pipe Maze! There is no explanation but you must get through the maze. It's easy to escape.
 Based on this video: https://youtu.be/BWXblAObfrg
A long and vegetable filled adventure. A mini Mario game I guess?
